Class ElementInfoWrapper<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mordoch.chemtools.util.elementinfo.ElementInfoWrapper<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AtomicNumberList, FamilyList, MassList, NameList, TypeList

    public abstract class ElementInfoWrapper<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class acts as a template for any class that hosts element information; it is most useful for the metadata. It is essentially a wrapper for a Map.
